X11=0

X01=0

#target = 1
for(i in 1:50){
  #
  new = a_test1[i,]
  pred=predict(model.bic,newdata=new)    #BIC
  val=exp(pred)/(1+exp(pred))               #1
  if(val>=0.5){
    X11=X11+1
  }else{
    X10=X10+1
  }
} 

#target = 0
for(i in 1:50){
  #
  new = a_test0[i,]
  pred=predict(model.bic,newdata=new)    #BIC
  val=exp(pred)/(1+exp(pred))            #0
  if(val<0.5){
    X00=X00+1
  }else{
    X01=X01+1
  }
}
